ld text-gray-900 mb-6","children":"ISO 45001 Certification in Dubai, UAE"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4","children":"Fundamentals of ISO 45001"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-700 mb-4","children":["ISO health and safety standard is the replacement of 18001, it makes coordination with other management systems easier than before; since it shares the new normal structure characterized by Annex SL, it is directly lined up with the 2015 revisions of ",["$","$Lf",null,{"href":"/iso-14001-certification-consultants-uae","className":"text-green-600 hover:text-green-800","children":"ISO 14001"}]," and ",["$","$Lf",null,{"href":"/iso-9001-certification-consultants-uae","className":"text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800","children":"ISO 9001"}],"."]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-700","children":["You can discover more data about ISO 45001: 2018 standard and better understand the difference between ",["$","$Lf",null,{"href":"/what-is-the-difference-between-OHSAS-18001-and-ISO-45001","className":"text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800","children":"ohsas 18001 iso 45001"}],". Existing OHSAS 18001 clients of Wizms, can get migration support and can implement and generate a gap analysis report that must be completed preceding a migration audit."]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-10 bg-orange-50 border-l-4 border-orange-500 p-6 rounded","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4","children":"Migration from OHSAS 18001 Certification"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-700 mb-4","children":"After achieving ISO 45001 certification, the OHSAS 18001 norms will be removed. A transition period of 3-years will be allotted to the OHSAS 18001 certified organizations. The guidelines defined by the International Accreditation Forum (IAF) have to be followed before migration from present OHSAS 18001 to ISO 45001 certification. Transition of OHSAS 18001 has to follow any of the two routes:"}],"$L10"]}],"$L11","$L12","$L13","$L14","$L15","$L16"]}]}],"$L17"]}]}]]}]
